\begin_layout Section

\lang bahasa
Boolean Logic in the OPAC 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\lang bahasa
Commencing with Senayan3-stable10, the OPAC search system supports boolean
 logic.
 In the search process the operators OR, NOT and AND can be used.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\lang bahasa
For example: subject = politic NOT politics, the result is politic without
 invoking politics.
 title = mapping AND author = Dwikorita , the result is a collection of
 titles containing the string 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

mapping
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 , and by author Dwikorita.
\end_layout

